  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The Hotel Levi Panorama is on a half board basis.</p>
<p>A varied continental breakfast is served each day, with hot and cold options.</p>
<p>Each evening you can enjoy a varied three course buffet with a variety of starters, hot dishes, salad buffet, selection of desserts and after dinner tea/coffee </p>
<p> </p>]]></cateringDescription>
