  <description><![CDATA[<p>This excellent hotel is in a idyllic location at the top of <a data-udi="umb://document/9dee14339770490983c23ccc11530d35" href="/{localLink:umb://document/9dee14339770490983c23ccc11530d35}" title="Santa Breaks in Levi">Levi</a> fell with wonderful wide-reaching views over the ski slopes, and the <span>nearby fells of Pallas and Kätkä</span>.<span> Overlooking the Levi Village, the hotel is easily accessible via the Levi Express Cabin lift, by stairs from the centre of the village or via road. </span><span></span></p>
<h2>Idyllic location</h2>
<p>You will get fantastic views across the snowy slopes at <a data-udi="umb://document/9dee14339770490983c23ccc11530d35" href="/{localLink:umb://document/9dee14339770490983c23ccc11530d35}" title="Santa Breaks in Levi">Levi Ski Resort</a>, as well as the fells that surround the resort, as the hotel is located at the top of the Levi fell. Exploring the resort of Levi is incredibly easy,  the convenient Levi Summit gondola, which is open from 9:30am to 11pm, is located right outside the hotel and takes less than five minutes to reach the centre of Levi. Plus, as a guest, you'll receive a free day ticket for each day of your stay (excluding the day of arrival or departure). </p>
<h2><span>Bright and spacious rooms and apartments</span></h2>
<p>The Panorama's spacious, well-equipped rooms can accommodate additional beds, providing comfort for the entire family after a day of exploring Levi; we recommend the Superior rooms which have a balcony with resort views, and also feature a drying closet, which is great for keeping your morning socks toasty. Alternatively the popular apartments are furnished in a modern style, offering greater space, additional bedrooms and a private sauna - perfect for warming up in after a day of Arctic adventures. As we have different occupancy apartments, they are ideal for a group of family and friends looking for self-catered apartments in <a data-udi="umb://document/a4a479e8266449e18b6b9e98eafdfcb0" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a4a479e8266449e18b6b9e98eafdfcb0}" title="Lapland Holidays">Lapland</a>.</p>
<h2>Family friendly facilities</h2>
<p>You'll find plenty of space to relax and recuperate in the excellent public areas. Children can have a great time making new friends in the play area, while the adults can relax and enjoy a refreshing drink in the bar or slope-side café. After a day of skiing or exploring Levi,  take some time to unwind and relax at the sauna-  It's the perfect place to warm up and rejuvenate. In addition, there is a wonderful restaurant with incredible views of the slopes, where you can enjoy your half board meals. The menu is inspired by traditional Lappish cuisine and features locally sourced ingredients.</p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>]]></description>
