  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Standard Rooms </strong>are around 28m<span>² </span>can sleep two to four people (recommended for three adults or two adults and two children) in twin beds, with a divan sofa bed which can be converted to two extra single beds for full occupancy. This room can be located on any floor and has a ski slope view. Standard rooms are also available for single occupancy at a supplement. </p>
<p><strong>Superior Rooms </strong>are around 33m<span>² and </span>can sleep two to four people (recommended for three adults or two adults and two children) in twin beds with a balcony and drying closet. There is a<span> divan sofa bed which can sleep either one adult or two children. Superior rooms can be l</span>ocated on any floor, facing the front hotel courtyard. Also available for single occupancy at a supplement. </p>
<p><strong>Standard Suite </strong>are around 52m<span>² and </span><span>can sleep two to four people. These Suites have a twin bedroom and a living area with a double sofa bed which can sleep one adult or two children, and a French </span><span>b</span>alcony (excluding some rooms on the 2nd floor) <span>facing the courtyard and Kätkä fell.</span><span></span><span></span></p>
<p>All of the hotel rooms are located in the main building and are furnished in a modern style.</p>
<p><strong>Room facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>TV</li>
<li>Tea and coffee making facilities</li>
<li>Minibar</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
<li>Shower</li>
<li>WC</li>
</ul>
<p> </p>
<p><strong>Panorama Apartments </strong></p>
<p><strong>One Bedroom Apartments </strong>are around 45-50m<span>² and </span>can sleep two to five people. These apartments have one twin bedroom plus an alcove with bunk beds (120cm double bed on lower bunk and single bed on upper bunk  - suitable for two adults or up to three children under 12yrs)</p>
<p><strong>Two Bedroom Apartments</strong> are around 65m<span>² </span>sleeping three to six people. These apartments have two twin bedrooms plus a double sofa bed in the living room (suitable for one adult or two children).</p>
<p>The apartments are located next to the main hotel building.</p>
<p><strong>Apartment facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Private sauna</li>
<li>Fully-equipped kitchen with fridge, oven, microwave, kettle, coffee maker, dishwasher and toaster plus washing machine</li>
<li>TV with DVD player</li>
<li>Radio</li>
<li>Safe</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
<li>Drying Closet</li>
<li>Private shower and WC</li>
<li>Linen and towels</li>
<li>End of stay cleaning</li>
</ul>
<p> </p>]]></roomsDescription>
